name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 29 – The Tarantula Ultimatum

content.html:
Dear Internet, This weeks episode was recorded in the corona time. This is the first time we’ve gotten to chat since all this went down so give us some slack as we get this out of our system. This week we talk about psychic vampires, eating a lot cheese, and when to issue the Tarantula Ultimatum. Thank you for reading this, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
